{"word":"ἄβουλος","slug":"ἄβουλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄβουλος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βουλή'><el>βουλή</el></a>\n<p/><i>inconsiderate, ill-advised</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τέκνοισι ἄβουλος</el> <i>taking no thought</i> for them, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>-ότερος</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ως</el>, <i>inconsiderately</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>ἀβουλότατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}